lead_paragraph: With no safety net in the bullpen, the New York Yankees needed a big lead and a long outing from starter Nathan Eovaldi to feel comfortable Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Eovaldi Pitches Yankees Past Price, Red Sox 8-2
